><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/w8IoggT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They’d been completely buried for so long, the community forgot they were there, and when the beach eroded, the originally thought it was an old wharf</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Z94bu4P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That’s a pretty curvy wharf though!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nmO7BN4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Here’s where a stream has cut between the main part of the ship, and the prow</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UM1Mrge.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Some of the ship’s internal structure was visible as well</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/t7lmkK2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Here’s the outline of 2 more, side by side under the shoreline</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ld3kWwc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>To give a sense of size, here’s a pic from 1925 - look at the person on the beach on the bottom right of the boat!! You can see one of the other ships beside it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8yiewcL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It was quite the ship in its day. The biggest of its kind ever built in Nova Scotia!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/yX8SCQD</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[drawnbyjohn]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Golden immediately becomes best friends with cat</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LHaUutr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/p2rV3Qq.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Let’s be honest, goldens become best friends with everything immediately</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LHaUutr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[tampacl]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>English Lesson</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/m8vB0eh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/R20b4UW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/m8vB0eh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SweepTheLeg31]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>turn based combat</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EpXlrgY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Uc8GkFL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/EpXlrgY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ilovetomakestuffup]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Bunny Happiness</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YdHWvEQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JboMMes.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/YdHWvEQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Baskerville84]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Party told you to reject the evidence of your eyes &amp; ears</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DFuN2vW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lKxmE4N.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sauce: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=24YZmMdJKmU</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DFuN2vW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SecretAgentSuperBooger]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>From the Texas senatorial debate</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pNW7yeh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yTDOs3C.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cruz truly is one of the biggest assholes in American politics, and just can’t hide it.</div></di